{"tid":997955,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★沙中線鋼筋拉力測試傳造假　絞牙長度特別製造","createTime":"2019-01-27T14:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T15:18:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec1b3986433d260f6c1376b946b1521641b85ba","tid":997955,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中線紅磡站獨立調查委員會的聆訊完結前夕，傳出鋼筋拉力測試造假。港鐵回應指，與政府商討後會確定測試內容，而測試會按照經同意的程序，在港鐵實驗室及獨立的實驗室進行，並會邀請政府部門代表見證測試。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，鋼筋實際測試與測試報告有出入，鋼筋樣本的絞牙長度是為測試而製造。另外，扭入螺絲帽的圈數亦多於報告的比例，以致更易通過測試。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人指，正如上星期調查委員會上提及，短期內會向政府及鐵路拓展處提交測試程序。東網正向屋宇署查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190127/bkn-20190127215135272-0127_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190127%2Fbkn-20190127215135272-0127_00822_001.html&d=pVnPKVlrfckw%2FdlZmyAw9%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=24c2f4ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190127/bkn-20190127215135272-0127_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"20654972199fa399f684cefd8af989610b3cd8a3","tid":997955,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"唔裝都得<br />\n咁仲洗乜做測試"},{"pid":"34918bcb1367535c9436c4961dd53e5636bf657e","tid":997955,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce1109bed48002a0237393393c7715f37716648","tid":997955,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}